&lt;h6&gt;加權股價指數近 6 個月價量表現：&lt;/h6&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;（資料來源：Bloomberg, 截至2023/2/22）&quot; data-height=&quot;167&quot; data-mime=&quot;image/png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;4.383233532934132&quot; data-src-m=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5094610/m/9dd68d8fad15cab3b0f4911b878095f1.jpg&quot; data-width=&quot;732&quot; src=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5094610/l/9dd68d8fad15cab3b0f4911b878095f1.jpg&quot;&gt;
